      "content": "**Overall scaffold**\n- One **anisole-like aromatic ring** (phenyl) bearing:\n  - **isopropoxy** substituent (CC(C)O\u2013): hydrophobic bulk\n  - **difluoromethoxy** substituent (\u2013OC(F)F): lipophilic, electron-withdrawing\n  - a **benzylic chiral side chain** linking to a heterocycle + another aromatic heteroaromatic",
