      "content": "**Heterocycles / aromatic domains**\n- **Thiazoline-like 5-member ring**: `C2=CN[C@@H](... )S2`  \n  Contains an **N\u2013H (amine-like)** and a **thioether (S)**; ring is partially unsaturated.\n- **Pyridine N-oxide**: `c2cc[n+]([O-])cc2`  \n  Aromatic, polar, **not basic** (the N is oxidized; no cation at phys pH).",
